## Debug

### Zombie agent (status=running but heartbeat stale >5min)

```bash
# Detect
curl -s "${HEADERS[@]}" \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/<id> | jq '{status, lastHeartbeatAt}'

# Recovery: pause + reset issue + force fresh session
curl -X PATCH "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"schedule":{"enabled":false}}' \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/<id>

# PATCH stuck issue to status=backlog, assigneeAgentId=null
curl -X PATCH "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"backlog","assigneeAgentId":null}' \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/issues/<id>

# Force wakeup on a different replica
curl -X POST "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"source":"on_demand","reason":"recovery zombie","forceFreshSession":true}' \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/<other-replica>/wakeup
```

### Read run logs

```bash
# List recent runs
curl -s "${HEADERS[@]}" \
  "$PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/heartbeat-runs?agentId=<id>&limit=10" | \
  jq '.[] | {id, startedAt, status, durationMs}'

# Full log of a run
curl -s "${HEADERS[@]}" \
  "$PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/heartbeat-runs/<run-id>/log?offset=0&limitBytes=50000" | \
  jq -r '.log'
```

### Cancel stale issue

```bash
curl -X PATCH "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"cancelled"}' \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/issues/<id>
```

### Pause `review-pending-prs` routine

```bash
curl -X PATCH "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"paused"}' \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/routines/$ROUTINE_REVIEW_PENDING_PRS_ID
```

