## Update AGENTS.md per-agent (after calibration / new lesson)

```bash
# Re-upload AGENTS-dev-primary.md to the 3 dev-primary
for id in $DEV_PRIMARY_1_ID $DEV_PRIMARY_2_ID $DEV_PRIMARY_3_ID; do
  curl -X PUT "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -d "$(jq -Rs '{path:"AGENTS.md",content:.}' < local/paperclip/AGENTS-dev-primary.md)" \
    $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/$id/instructions-bundle/file
done

# Re-upload AGENTS-reviewer.md to the reviewer
curl -X PUT "${HEADERS[@]}" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d "$(jq -Rs '{path:"AGENTS.md",content:.}' < local/paperclip/AGENTS-reviewer.md)" \
  $PAPERCLIP_API_BASE/api/agents/$REVIEWER_ID/instructions-bundle/file
```

