## Renew Paperclip token (if expired)

On the droplet:

```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/<your-droplet-key> paperclip@<your-droplet-ip>
npx paperclipai auth login --api-base http://127.0.0.1:3100
# (interactive; opens URL for Pilot to approve in browser)
cat ~/.paperclip/auth.json
# Copy token to local ~/.config/<your-project>/paperclip.env (mode 600)
```

