## Anthropic quota check

On the droplet:

```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/<your-droplet-key> paperclip@<your-droplet-ip>
claude /usage
# Shows rolling 5h Sonnet + rolling 7d Opus
# If Sonnet > 80% near a big wave, wait 1-2h or pause another project sharing the OAuth subscription
```

