## Droplet health + backup

```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/<your-droplet-key> paperclip@<your-droplet-ip>

# Disk
df -h /home/paperclip

# Backup sizes (if you have them)
ls -lh ~/backups/ 2>/dev/null | tail -5

# pm2 status (if you run paperclip via pm2)
pm2 status

# Recent paperclip logs
pm2 logs paperclip --lines 50

# If paperclip hung
pm2 restart paperclip
```
